      • unmarshalJson

        public static <T extends VersionedData> T unmarshalJson(VersionedDataKind<T> kind,
                                                        java.lang.String data)
        Unmarshals a feature store item from a JSON string. This is a very simple wrapper around a Gson method, just to allow external feature store implementations to make use of the Gson instance that's inside the SDK rather than having to import Gson themselves.
        Type Parameters:
        T - class of the object that will be returned
        Parameters:
        kind - specifies the type of item being decoded
        data - the JSON string
        Returns:
        the unmarshaled item
        Throws:
        FeatureStoreHelpers.UnmarshalException - if the JSON string was invalid

      • marshalJson

        Marshals a feature store item into a JSON string. This is a very simple wrapper around a Gson method, just to allow external feature store implementations to make use of the Gson instance that's inside the SDK rather than having to import Gson themselves.
        Parameters:
        item - the item to be marshaled
        Returns:
        the JSON string
